pment of interfaces (UI, UX, IxD), applying responsive design to render well on a variety of devices and window or screen sizes, and using jQuery library for dynamic applications. I have great knowledge of the use of Angular / Cli and AngularJS as JavaScript framework for the creation of front-end web applications.\\nIn addition, I have experience in the development of web applications that work with PHP for the development of the server side, being able to develop the workflow and creating communication with the database. I also have knowledge about the open-source JavaScript platform NOde.js and in languages such as Python and Java.\\n\\nIn addition, I have experience working with database managers based on relational models such as SQLSERVER, PostgreSQL, MySQL and non-SQL database managers such as Mongo DB, defining and implementing database backup and recovery procedures, performance tuning and implementing database change management procedure.\\n\\nI have knowledge about the use of Git as a tool for the control of project versions, for the coordination of teamwork, monitoring of the changes made in the project and updating changes made. I also have experience working on any operating system, both UNIX and Debian, Ubuntu, Elementary OS, as the most well known operating systems Windows and OS X.\\n\\n\\u003c/div\\u003e\",\"text_selected_editor\":\"html\",\"autop\":true,\"_sow_form_id\":\"11502760815cc31b312a4da679404774\",\"_sow_form_timestamp\":\"1556294159936\",\"panels_info\":{\"class\":\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\",\"grid\":0,\"cell\":1,\"id\":3,\"widget_id\":\"001b1f8b-455d-4526-af26-102ebaeb35ce\",\"style\":{\"background_image_attachment\":false,\"background_display\":\"tile\"}}}],\"grids\":[{\"cells\":2,\"style\":{\"background_image_attachment\":false,\"background_display\":\"tile\",\"cell_alignment\":\"flex-start\"},\"ratio\":1,\"ratio_direction\":\"right\"},{\"cells\":2,\"style\":{\"background_image_attachment\":false,\"background_display\":\"tile\